# 864e593259f34373adcc6d170f3aa881
#: ../../introduction.txt:4
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "簡介"

# 0046061e6d924cbc81221c5b08312f94
#: ../../introduction.txt:6
msgid ""
"PortaBase is a small database program for creating, browsing, and editing "
"custom tables of data.  Typical uses are media inventories, reference "
"charts, TODO lists, shopping lists, etc.  Notable features include:"
msgstr "PortaBase是一個可以用來新增、瀏覽與編輯任意資料表的小型程式。典型的使用方式包含媒體清單、參考圖表、待辦事項清單、購物清單等等。它包含下列特點："

# 8f9f1193b22d4850b6573ee9980761b6
#: ../../introduction.txt:8
msgid ""
"String, Integer, Decimal, Boolean, Note (multi-line text), Date, Time, "
"Calculation, Sequence, Image, and Enum column types"
msgstr "支援字串、整數、十進數、布林值、多行文字項、日期、時間, 影像 與集合等欄位型別"

# 41732c117431468cb92e4621b49011e4
#: ../../introduction.txt:10
msgid "Custom data views (subsets of the columns in any order)"
msgstr "任意的資料景觀(由任何數目的欄位依照任意順序組合而成)"

# 713920e22e284a5fa9b5fa09e58131a9
#: ../../introduction.txt:12
msgid "Filter the displayed rows using sets of conditions"
msgstr "可使用多個條件來進行篩選並顯示結果"

# 9b402b247414438680443c4428ed6075
#: ../../introduction.txt:14
msgid ""
"Sort the rows by any combination of columns, each in ascending or descending"
" order"
msgstr "可依照任意欄位的組合來加以排序，其中每個欄位可指定順序遞增或遞減"

# 32e170ec57bb480689a39df26f8ac923
#: ../../introduction.txt:16
msgid ""
"Good performance even when browsing large tables; the display only loads "
"data as needed"
msgstr "良好的性能，即使瀏覽大型表，顯示只需要加載數據"

# 54a7420316524ea5a3b213a2b01f9010
#: ../../introduction.txt:18
msgid "Optional page navigation buttons, with custom number of rows per page"
msgstr "可設定每頁顯示幾列，並具有頁面瀏覽鈕"

# 593d17994b1e4632a1663803d1b5c7f5
#: ../../introduction.txt:20
msgid "Add, delete, rearrange, and rename columns at any time"
msgstr "任何時刻皆可對欄位進行新增、刪除、重排與重新命名的動作"

# 07272370c9944b0cab739b88114bd731
#: ../../introduction.txt:22
msgid "Specify default values for columns"
msgstr "指定欄位的預設值"

# a00bb7d1079042e2a4e66197960b128b
#: ../../introduction.txt:24
msgid "View summary statistics for columns (total, average, min, max, etc.)"
msgstr "檢視欄位的統計資訊(加總、平均、最小值與最大值等)"

# bf197da1ddaa4d9497817087cc44c166
#: ../../introduction.txt:26
msgid "Import data from CSV, XML, and MobileDB files"
msgstr "可匯入CSV、XML與MobileDB格式的檔案"

# 215b3a3e261748a290db78acb9915dfc
#: ../../introduction.txt:28
msgid "Export data to CSV, HTML, and XML files"
msgstr "外出資料到CSV, HTML, 和XML 檔案"

# 0326c943737f4cc8935f66a008385922
#: ../../introduction.txt:30
msgid ""
"Command-line format conversions (to and from XML, to and from CSV, from "
"MobileDB, to HTML)"
msgstr "命令行的格式轉換(去和從 XML, 去和從CSV, 從 mobileDB, 轉到HTML)"

# a2443ec58e824e2cb95acafb810b94fd
#: ../../introduction.txt:32
msgid ""
"Print the data grid with view, sorting, and filter applied (not supported on"
" Maemo)"
msgstr "打印數據網格認為，排序和過濾器適用於（不支持Maemo操作）"

# cde87a7997da42c79fd5c9f9aca30fba
#: ../../introduction.txt:34
msgid "Fullscreen mode option"
msgstr "全屏模式選項"

# a25b4e13cb6b4c9091314367de03072e
#: ../../introduction.txt:36
msgid "Optional data file encryption"
msgstr "可以選擇的資料檔案加密"

# 629eabc2bb704b9dbc57fd3f34105c13
#: ../../introduction.txt:38
msgid "Unicode support"
msgstr "支援Unicode"

# e0de9c1511d54ddc805f1cafd993f5db
#: ../../introduction.txt:40
msgid ""
"Pick any available font to use throughout the application (not supported on "
"Mac OS X)"
msgstr "整體程式作品可以選擇任何一個可以用的字體從一而終(但Mac OS X  不支持)"

# 60332a09ecbd4c2ca68b01dbdfa41ecd
#: ../../introduction.txt:42
msgid ""
"User-specified alternating row background colors (Maemo Fremantle uses "
"colors from the system theme instead)"
msgstr "使用者指定交替行背景顏色(Maemo Fremantle 使用系統主題顏色）"

# d68b7b5cdb524dd6a2cdf85abcc482f2
#: ../../introduction.txt:44
msgid "Simple calculator widget for entering numeric data"
msgstr "簡單的計算機元件便於輸入數值資料"
